PrecisAuthority to enter into AMENDING AGREEMENT NO. 9 with the Provinces for the purpose of implementing changes to the NET INCOME STABILIZATION ACCOUNT PROGRAM which allows for (a) greater flexibility for the producers in exercising their deposit and withdrawal options, and (b) producers who have opted out of the program to rejoin it in two years instead of three.
